{
  "stem": "17135.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 291.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the-- the Poles didn't want to take them in, and the Germans didn't want to take them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were in Niemandsland-- in no man's land-- for two or three days, and then thousands were deported to Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my two brothers-- the older brothers-- they were deported to Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was really frightening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were just lucky, my father and myself, that-- that that happened a few hours, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Whoever they caught got caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were lucky we're not caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we knew that all the promises that the Nazis made throughout the years that they will destroy the Jews, they will take care of the Jews, that they really did it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was an indestructible optimist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On many occasions when we read in the German newspapers what Hitler predicted, what Goebbels predicted, it just-- it's just politics.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The world, the civilized world, is never going to tolerate this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was such an optimist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's the reason why we really didn't make a serious effort to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we had enough means financially.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did very well, because-- I give you an example.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gymnasium and lyceum, you have to pay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very expensive in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's almost like a university here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And her younger brother, in-- in Palestine at that time, made several times phone calls and letters we should sell everything and go into paint, because he married into a family.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a paint factory in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and IG Farben was famous, world famous, for inventing new paints, new-- new-- let's put it this-- kind of paints that were superior to other paints.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, buy yourself paints, and we open up and-- and you join his family in a paint factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
